data.title: Improving the Quality of Life
meta_keywords: United States of America development work
data.meta_description: The Aga Khan Development Network (AKDN) is dedicated to improving the quality of life of those in need.
data.text:
The Aga Khan Development Network (AKDN) is dedicated to improving the quality of life of those in need, mainly in Asia and Africa, irrespective of their origin, faith, or gender. Our multifaceted development approach aims to help communities and individuals become self-reliant.

Honouring Cultural Heritage

We invest in heritage, architecture and the arts to enable communities to build on their past and look to the future with confidence.
